Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.67,0:00:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to see Kamijou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.84,0:00:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry. We've arranged a new treatment for him. He's in the rehabilitation room right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.53,0:00:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She always comes by to pay him a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.44,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That patient is a real handful. We're lucky to have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she can do something for him.{TLC: "that girl"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before the accident, he was a child prodigy with the violin.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.64,0:00:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he's able to walk again, his fingers will prevent him from being able to play music.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.75,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it have to be Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.86,0:01:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how well my fingers work, they'll never do me any good. {TLC: "no matter how lively"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.28,0:01:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did this have to happen to him instead of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.24,0:01:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's able to recover thanks to my wish, how would that make him feel? {TLC: "how would he look upon this matter?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.89,0:01:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would it be a mere, "thank you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something more that I want him to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.15,0:01:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.57,0:01:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a bad girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back now, I didn't understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't understand a thing about miracles. Nor did I understand the price I would have to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.30,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4\bord0\an1\fad(236,0)\c&H6B6E73&\pos(338,489)}Episode 4   There Exists Both Miracles and Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.55,0:03:21.30,EPISODE TITLE,SIGN,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(236,0)\pos(334,483)\c&HFDFDFD&}Episode 4  {\c&HF1FCFC&} There Exists Both Miracles and Magic
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.60,0:03:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got something there.{did I time this right? -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't start eating, you'll be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:03:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.63,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-chan, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the food that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.28,0:04:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.38,0:04:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Papa's cooking is so delicious because I'm alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.76,0:04:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what I said after that, there was no response.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even worked up some tears and asked if I had said something weird again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really hard not to burst out laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.01,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, about what happened yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, not right now. We can talk about it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm weird, am I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.14,0:04:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of nitrates and hot springs, we must refer back to our medical science for the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}However, based on what we've seen, the estimated number of people living in poverty is largely inaccurate.{TLC Note: "By that calculation, poverty estimates are hugely mistaken."}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, females above the age of 30 may still have a chance to fall in love and get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.54,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, the correct form to use here is the present tense rather than the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.44,0:05:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like we somehow ended up in an unfamiliar land.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.89,0:05:40.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school where we met Hitomi-chan is exactly the same as yesterday. {QC I don't hear Mami but Hitomi-chan, so I replaced it}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everywhere you look, there are strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.16,0:05:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know about Magical Girls and Mami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But everyone else is oblivious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:06:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're living in a different world, and the things we see are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.83,0:06:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything changed a long time ago. We should have realized it sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, do you still intend to become a Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We knew this wasn't going to be easy. We can't just back out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.45,0:06:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I think about the way she died, I feel like I'm suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm scared. I don't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mami-san was a very kind and gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How disillusioned must one be to do battle? In order to show us that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.22,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...she...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyubei, where will this road lead us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.67,0:07:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who will take Mami-san's place and protect everyone from the Witches?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:20.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This has always been Mami's territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.72,0:07:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that there's nobody guarding it, the other Magical Girls won't just sit back and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There will soon be others coming to deal with the Witches here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.76,0:07:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they be in it just for the grief seeds?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.27,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that transfer student.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that people like Mami are rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most would first weigh the pros and cons before acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants something.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.30,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But only those who also carry the burden of being a Magical Girl have the right to criticize them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.88,0:07:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand what you're thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:08:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it is unfortunate, I can't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.23,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's end things here. I need to search for more people who will form a contract with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.19,0:08:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Kyubei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should be the one apologizing. I shouldn't have gotten you mixed up in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a short journey, but I still want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.23,0:08:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun living with you, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.65,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that I'm so useless. I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname Madoka, you're blaming yourself too much for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one who can criticize you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone were to, I wouldn't let them go easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you listen to what I have to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.49,0:09:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I had listened to you earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.85,0:10:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still would not have been able to affect the fate of Tomoe Mami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.56,0:10:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But your fate has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.17,0:10:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can only save one person, that is enough to make me truly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan seems to have experienced happiness, but it's kinda different from Mami-san's type. {OKAY SERIOUSLY THIS MAKES NO SENSE NEEDS TLC}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.86,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's very likely. I won't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already seen lots of people die like that, right? Just like that scene from yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.95,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.66,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too many to bother counting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will that room remain as it is forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomoe Mami has no relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.28,0:10:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine it will be a while before anyone reports her missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.17,0:11:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will know that Mami-san is dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.55,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't leave behind a corpse if you die in that world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, she is merely a lost soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.50,0:11:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the fate of all Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.21,0:11:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was always fighting alone to protect everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to think that nobody will ever know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.45,0:11:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all have made the contract and received this power.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not meant for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we can do is stand for what we believe in and continue to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if nobody recognizes us, and nobody remembers who we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nothing that we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.05,0:12:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.50,0:12:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget Mami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.70,0:12:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.37,0:12:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that would make her very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.71,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan too! I definitely won't forget you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.64,0:12:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forget how you saved us yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.71,0:12:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're too kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must remember that this kindness may lead you into even greater pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.05,0:13:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you listening to?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieder und Gesänge. {若き日の歌?} {wat TLC please}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Debussy? {taken from http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mahler} {wat on earth? she clearly says Debussy}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a beautiful piece, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.63,0:13:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most people don't expect me to be interested in classical music.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.07,0:13:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So when I tell them that I know the name of a piece, they're always really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's kind of unexpected, and they respect me for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.69,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyousuke, if you hadn't shown these to me, I probably never would have heard them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka, do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.53,0:13:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?{added, masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.46,0:14:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still making me listen to music?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.77,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to hurt me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you like music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.34,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to listen to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just listening to music when I can't even play...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.57,0:14:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't move them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't feel pain at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.05,0:14:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These hands are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.89,0:14:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.24,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose hope. They'll heal someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was told to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The doctor came in-person and told me to give up on music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.12,0:14:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said it's not possible with the current technology.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My hands will never move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.37,0:15:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless miracles or magic exist, they won't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.23,0:15:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miracles and magic do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have made friends with Homura-chan if I had talked to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was she fighting with Mami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hitomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About today's homework!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.87,0:15:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's just like the woman from that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.17,0:15:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Hitomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.39,0:15:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Kaname-san. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.82,0:15:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I going...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to a place that's much better than this.{split -masat}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.82,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hitomi-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know! Why don't you come with me, Kaname-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.19,0:16:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. That would be splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.49,0:16:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could just contact Homura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.59,0:16:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know her phone number!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:50.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... I'm useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't even run a small factory correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:16:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way I am now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.99,0:17:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no place to go to.
