Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.67,0:17:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you mix these together, something bad will happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.39,0:17:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could kill everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mustn't mix them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.67,0:17:31.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be imprudent to interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.07,0:17:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a ritual of offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.68,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone here will die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Everyone here will soon embark on a journey through wonderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand how wonderful that would be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A living body is nothing more than a hindrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.85,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaname-san, you will come to understand soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.17,0:18:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.35,0:18:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.20,0:19:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this my punishment?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.66,0:19:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm weak? Because I'm a liar?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to pay the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This should finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.39,0:20:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I made it just in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan, that costume...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you could say I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! I did well for my first time, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Transfer Student!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.33,0:21:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd actually come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard about that Mami going and getting herself killed, so I made the trip out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.09,0:22:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here? This is completely different from what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.84,0:22:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry about that. The city has a new Magical Girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.17,0:22:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only just formed the contract with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.25,0:22:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.48,0:22:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty pissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.80,0:22:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I would just give up on such a suitable breeding ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.29,0:22:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you even need to ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just need to beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.62,0:22:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl...
